            <!-- Subtle primary glow -->
            <div class="absolute -top-20 -left-20 w-40 h-40 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>
            
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-accent">Technical Approach</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
              What sets us apart is our hybrid approach - combining deep coding expertise with no-code and low-code automation tools. This allows us to tackle complex automation challenges that might be beyond the scope of traditional solutions.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
